General.Name: Garda Capital Group
General.Description: Green Critical Minerals Limited engages in the exploration and development of mineral properties in Australia and Canada. It explores for graphite, topaz, tungsten, nickel, copper, cobalt, gold, and platinum group elements. The company was formerly known as Chase Mining Corporation Limited and changed its name to Green Critical Minerals Limited in December 2022. Green Critical Minerals Limited was incorporated in 2006 and is based in Brisbane, Australia.
